NAME
    CPAN::Webserver - Browse and search CPAN locally

SYNOPSIS
      % cpan_webserver

DESCRIPTION
    This module allows you to browse and search a CPAN mirror. It
    automatically tries to find a locally-configured CPAN mirror using
    CPAN::Mirror::Finder.

